files.description: Full HTML of the EHI export documentation page. Contains the entire export documentation: description of C-CDA format, list of 17 included C-CDA sections, and links to HL7 C-CDA 2.2 StructureDefinitions. No downloadable files or data dictionary.

WordPress REST API JSON response for the EHI export page. Contains structured page metadata (published 2023-11-16, modified 2023-12-05) and rendered HTML content. The content field contains the same documentation as the HTML page but in a cleaner form without navigation/theme markup.
Full-page screenshot of the EHI export documentation page showing all content: header, Getting Started section, Terms and Conditions, and Data Included section with the list of 17 C-CDA sections.
Viewport screenshot of the top of the EHI export documentation page showing the page header and beginning of the Getting Started section.
